     * The ktlint-suppression rule can not be suppressed via any mechanism. It is the rule that detects and replaces old-style ktlint
     * suppression directives (ktlint-disable/ktlint-enable) with @Suppress annotations. Suppressing this rule would make it impossible
     * to replace the old-style directives.
     */
    private val KTLINT_SUPPRESSION_RULE_ID = RuleId("standard:ktlint-suppression")

